---

<section class="activities-overview">
  <div class="l-container-s">
    <div class="l-section">
      <div class="activities-overview-title">
        <div class="c-title">
          <h2 class="c-title-ja">事業概要</h2>
          <span class="c-title-en" aria-hidden="true">Overview</span>
        </div><!-- /.c-title -->
      </div><!-- /.activities-overview-title -->

      <div class="l-section-body">
        <div class="activities-overview-title-lv3">
          <h3 class="c-heading-md c-heading-md--green">学生に、社会と協働するチャンスを</h3>
        </div><!-- /.activities-overview-title-lv3 -->
        <div class="activities-overview-lead">
          <p class="activities-overview-lead-text">社会に出ないと実現できないと、先入観で諦めてしまいがちな「これがしたい」という想い。<br>Oita Campus Linkは、社会人の皆さまにご協力いただきながら、学生が社会と関わり、価値を提供する経験ができる「挑戦のチャンス」を学生に届けることを目的に活動しています。</p>
          <p class="activities-overview-lead-text">学生と社会人が対等に関わる場を設計し、その出会いから実践的な取り組みが生まれるまでを支援しています。</p>
        </div><!-- /.activities-overview-lead -->

        <ul class="activities-overview-list">
          <li class="activities-overview-item">
            <div class="activities-overview-title-lv4">
              <p class="activities-overview-title-sub c-heading-sm c-heading-sm--sub-green">出会いを設計する</p>
              <h4 class="activities-overview-title-main c-heading-md">交流会の企画・運営</h4>
            </div><!-- /.activities-overview-title-lv4 -->
            <div class="activities-overview-image">
              <img src="/assets/images/activities/pic-activities-overview-01@2x.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="310" height="200">
            </div><!-- /.activities-overview-image -->
            <div class="activities-overview-description">
              <p class="activities-overview-description-text">Oita Campus Linkが主催し、学生同士だけでなく社会人も交えた交流の場を開催しています。</p>
              <p class="activities-overview-description-text">学年や立場を越えた対話を通じて、互いの価値観や取り組みを知り、連携や挑戦につながる「出会いのきっかけ」を生み出します。</p>
            </div><!-- /.activities-overview-description -->
          </li>
          <li class="activities-overview-item">
            <div class="activities-overview-title-lv4">
              <p class="activities-overview-title-sub c-heading-sm c-heading-sm--sub-green">連携の具体化</p>
              <h4 class="activities-overview-title-main c-heading-md">学生と社会をつなぐ共創支援</h4>
            </div><!-- /.activities-overview-title-lv4 -->
            <div class="activities-overview-image">
              <img src="/assets/images/activities/pic-activities-overview-02@2x.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="310" height="200">
            </div><!-- /.activities-overview-image -->
            <div class="activities-overview-description">
              <p class="activities-overview-description-text">交流会などで生まれたつながりを起点に、企業・行政と学生が協力する取り組みが生まれています。</p>
              <p class="activities-overview-description-text">Oita Campus Linkは、企画の相談や情報整理、必要に応じた伴走を通じて、学生と社会の連携が形になるまでをサポートします。</p>
            </div><!-- /.activities-overview-description -->
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div><!-- /.l-section-body -->
    </div><!-- /.l-section -->
  </div><!-- /.l-container-s -->
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../../styles/breakpoints' as *;

  .activities-overview-title {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .activities-overview-lead {
    margin-block-start: 32px;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .activities-overview-lead-text {
    & + & {
      margin-block-start: 16px;
    }
  }

  .activities-overview-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-block-start: 32px;
  }

  .activities-overview-item {
    display: grid;
    gap: 32px;
    padding-block: 40px;
    padding-inline: calc(20px / var(--width-sp) * 100vw);
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .activities-overview-title-main {
    margin-block-start: 4px;
  }

  .activities-overview-description {
    text-align: justify;
  }

  @include mq() {
    .activities-overview-lead {
      margin-block-start: 40px;
    }

    .activities-overview-list {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      margin-block-start: 40px;
    }

    .activities-overview-item {
      display: grid;
      gap: 32px;
      padding-block: 40px;
      padding-inline: 24px;
      background-color: var(--color-white);
    }

    .activities-overview-title-main {
      margin-block-start: 4px;
    }

    .activities-overview-description {
      text-align: justify;
    }
  }
</style>
